 {
  coords 2044.063 3.122 828.46
  m_sTitle "SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "Our unit is in a staging position (GRID REF:015 023) preparing to conduct a river crossing."\
  "We are an understrength company sized group, armed with PKMs, AK74s, SVDs and RPGs.  We have brought a bmp1 along for fire support. We have no dedicated crew. Our unit has access to a FPV kit with 2x drones. This is available in a box near the spawn, and can be given to whoever CO likes."\
  ""\
  "Enemy is a platoon sized infantry unit, armed with L85s, GPMGs, Carl Gustavs and DMRs. Wearing multicam camo."\
  ""\
  "Command has tasked us with seizing a route across the river to enable an assault by follow on forces onto a nearby town being used to stage supplies for this section of the front."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
